nodes.text: "High Noon on Jakku" is a short story by Landry Q. Walker that was published as an eBook on December 1, 2015, and was later published in print inside the anthology Tales from a Galaxy Far, Far Away: Aliens: Volume I on April 5, 2016. The story was written like a classic western.
A renegade droid causes problems for Constable Zuvio on Jakku.
